room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: Very challenging! Great for team building! We had 15 players and split up between two rooms and everyone had a blast! Can't wait to go back!

room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: Awesome room, true to theme, spacious, with a lot of puzzles and interesting locks/tech. Quality place!

room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: Super fun room! Very realistic, great set design and clever puzzles! Highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: We LOVED the Murder Motel - it was really well done and a ton of fun. We had 8 people in our group and it was fantastic to be able split up as needed. Definitely worth the visit!

room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: The Murder Motel was tons of fun for everyone. The instructor was great and made us feel very welcome. It was challenging and well set up. I definitely recommend everyone to check them out. It was a trip to remember!

room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: This was a great room (The Motel)! We have done several rooms and this one was legit! Highly recommended!

room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: This was my third escape room experience and it was wonderful. We were welcomed warmly and chatted with the owners for a little while afterwards. Thank you so much!

room_title: Escape room "The Murder Motel" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
review: One of the best escape rooms in the area. Very realistic looking room, clever puzzles, and a few surprising elements. Really enjoyed this room, can't wait for more from Enter Locked!
